  "title": "Service Engineer, $3,500 (MacPherson)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location: MacPherson</strong></p><p><strong>Salary: $3,500</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Provide on-site installation, maintenance, troubleshooting, and technical support for machines, including Laser Processing Machines and PCB Drilling Machines.</li><li>Ensure timely and effective service to achieve high customer satisfaction.</li><li>Prepare reports and document customer interactions thoroughly.</li><li>Keep updated with the latest technologies and industry trends to provide proactive support.</li><li>Demonstrate flexibility in handling technical challenges.</li><li>Carry out other technical or engineering-related tasks as assigned by management.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Mechanical Engineering, Electrical Engineering, or a related field.</li><li>At least 3 years of experience as a Service Engineer, Service Technician, or in a similar technical support and maintenance role.</li><li>Strong technical knowledge of mechanical and electronic systems and components.</li><li>Understanding of safety standards and protocols when working with machinery and equipment.</li><li>Excellent problem-solving and diagnostic abilities.</li><li>Customer-oriented mindset with strong communication and interpersonal skills.</li><li>Ability to work independently as well as collaboratively within a team.</li><li>Willingness to work overtime or on weekends when required.</li></ul><p>Interested applicants, please email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:lilian@juhlerprofessionals.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">lilian@juhlerprofessionals.com.sg</a></p><p>Tan Li Lian</p><p>EA 01C3135</p><p>Reg R1100465</p>",
